BehTalk is a practice project for working with Node.js, Mongodb and Express framework.

New users can  create account in /create route , and saving their data's in mongo database.
they can log in and send their message in /sending route to specified user by email.
The app (server) listening on port 4000.

localhost:4000
localhost:4000/create
localhost:4000/login
localhost:4000/sending
localhost:4000/delete
localhost:4000/update
